  "body": "*Title*: *Support extracting downstream Port in header variables*\r\n\r\n*Description*:\r\n\r\nAdd support for extracting/injecting Port information of the downstream local address in the header formater. Similarly to %DOWNSTREAM_LOCAL_ADDRESS% and %DOWNSTREAM_LOCAL_ADDRESS_WITHOUT_PORT%, but for Port only.\r\n\r\nOur use case: We inject a set of custom headers and heavily rely on envoy to extract/inject information about TLS and downstream addresses into those headers. In order to fully support our scenario we need to be able to extract downstream port information without the downstream address itself.  \r\n\r\n[optional *Relevant Links*:]\r\n- https://www.envoyproxy.io/docs/envoy/latest/configuration/http/http_conn_man/headers.html?highlight=downstream_local_address#custom-request-response-headers\r\n\r\n\r\n",
